1
00:00:00,959 --> 00:00:02,836
[Marcus] <i>According to NLEA's report,</i>

2
00:00:02,919 --> 00:00:05,797
<i>somewhere in the seas</i>
<i>of Zamboanga Peninsula,</i>

3
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:08,883
<i>illegal and smuggled firearms were dumped.</i>

4
00:00:08,967 --> 00:00:11,302
<i>That's Datu Rahman Abubakar.</i>

5
00:00:11,386 --> 00:00:14,097
[Lara] <i>He's been working in</i>
<i>the gun smuggling syndicate for a decade.</i>

6
00:00:14,180 --> 00:00:16,808
<i>He has perfected a system</i>
<i>to avoid investigations.</i>

7
00:00:16,891 --> 00:00:20,145
[Marcus] <i>Our mission</i>
<i>is to capture and arrest</i>

8
00:00:20,228 --> 00:00:21,688
<i>Datu Rahman Abubakar.</i>

9
00:00:21,771 --> 00:00:25,692
<i>We will only use force</i>
<i>and weapons when necessary.</i>

10
00:00:25,775 --> 00:00:28,820
<i>We are not going to that island to kill.</i>

11
00:00:28,903 --> 00:00:29,863
[Jamilah] <i>Jalil!</i>

12
00:00:29,946 --> 00:00:31,531
[Jalil] <i>I was only gone for three months</i>

13
00:00:31,614 --> 00:00:33,867
<i>to train new members of the CDSU.</i>

14
00:00:33,950 --> 00:00:36,119
<i>Not ten years.</i>

15
00:00:36,202 --> 00:00:40,749
[Datu] <i>The syndicate hasn't stopped</i>
<i>dumping weapons</i>

16
00:00:40,832 --> 00:00:41,833
<i>in the sea near us.</i>

17
00:00:41,916 --> 00:00:43,042
These weapons…

18
00:00:43,126 --> 00:00:46,379
We'll bury these and forget.

19
00:00:46,463 --> 00:00:49,924
[tense music]

20
00:00:50,008 --> 00:00:51,676
[Marcus] <i>Visual confirmation</i>
<i>of Datu Rahman.</i>

21
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:53,678
- [Lara] <i>Copy.</i>
- [Marcus] <i>Something's wrong.</i>

22
00:00:53,762 --> 00:00:55,180
<i>The area's full of civilians.</i>

23
00:00:55,263 --> 00:00:56,681
[Felix] <i>Neutralize the area!</i>

24
00:00:56,765 --> 00:00:59,184
<i>There are no civilians there!</i>
<i>They'll ambush you!</i>

25
00:00:59,267 --> 00:01:02,812
- [gunshots]
- [people screaming]

26
00:01:02,896 --> 00:01:04,606
Agent Reyes, do you hear me?

27
00:01:04,689 --> 00:01:06,608
[Datu] <i>Why are you doing this?!</i>

28
00:01:06,691 --> 00:01:09,235
<i>We are not your enemy!</i>

29
00:01:09,319 --> 00:01:10,862
- [sobbing]
- [Datu shouts]

30
00:01:12,238 --> 00:01:14,491
We will fight!

31
00:01:14,574 --> 00:01:15,575
Father!

32
00:01:15,658 --> 00:01:16,493
- [gunshots]
- [grunts]

33
00:01:16,576 --> 00:01:17,786
They're raining bullets on us, sir!

34
00:01:17,869 --> 00:01:19,537
[gunfire]

35
00:01:21,664 --> 00:01:22,916
[Marcus] What are you doing?!

36
00:01:23,583 --> 00:01:25,835
A lot of innocent people
will die from what you're doing!

37
00:01:25,919 --> 00:01:28,922
[tense music]

38
00:01:35,220 --> 00:01:38,473
[mysterious theme music playing]

39
00:01:50,485 --> 00:01:52,237
- [rapid gunfire]
- [people screaming]

40
00:01:59,619 --> 00:02:02,455
[In Arabic] God is great! God is great!

41
00:02:02,539 --> 00:02:06,000
[child cries]

42
00:02:06,876 --> 00:02:08,044
[Jalil grunts]

43
00:02:10,213 --> 00:02:12,507
[women screaming]

44
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:15,051
[rapid gunfire]

45
00:02:18,513 --> 00:02:22,267
- [child shouting]
- Run! Run!

46
00:02:23,852 --> 00:02:26,980
- [man yelling] God is great!
- [rapid gunfire]

47
00:02:27,063 --> 00:02:28,148
[man shouts]

48
00:02:28,231 --> 00:02:30,441
[grunting and groaning]

49
00:02:30,525 --> 00:02:31,734
Domingo!

50
00:02:31,818 --> 00:02:33,778
[shouting and screaming]

51
00:02:36,698 --> 00:02:39,367
[woman] Cross! Quick, cross!

52
00:02:39,450 --> 00:02:42,453
[gunshots]

53
00:02:42,537 --> 00:02:43,580
[woman shrieks]

54
00:02:48,126 --> 00:02:49,085
[man shouts] God is great!

55
00:02:49,168 --> 00:02:52,505
[rapid gunfire]

56
00:02:52,589 --> 00:02:54,591
[shouting]

57
00:02:59,304 --> 00:03:00,722
[grunting]

58
00:03:00,805 --> 00:03:03,266
[groans]

59
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:06,603
Let's go!

60
00:03:07,395 --> 00:03:10,148
Run! Hurry! Run!

61
00:03:10,231 --> 00:03:11,482
[monitor whirring]

62
00:03:11,566 --> 00:03:12,901
[Lara] What the hell is happening?

63
00:03:12,984 --> 00:03:15,528
[shouting]

64
00:03:17,488 --> 00:03:19,782
Fix my visuals! Where's my visuals?

65
00:03:19,866 --> 00:03:21,701
Fix the satellite now!

66
00:03:23,369 --> 00:03:26,080
- [grunting]
- [gunshots]

67
00:03:29,709 --> 00:03:31,419
[groaning]

68
00:03:32,754 --> 00:03:35,924
[tense music playing]

69
00:03:36,007 --> 00:03:37,717
Mama! Let's go, Mama!

70
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:40,136
[woman] No! Leave without me!

71
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:42,513
Go! Take the children!

72
00:03:42,597 --> 00:03:45,683
[rapid gunfire]

73
00:03:54,317 --> 00:03:56,361
Mama, let's go! Mama!

74
00:03:57,070 --> 00:04:00,490
[woman] No! Go! Leave without me! Hurry!

75
00:04:00,573 --> 00:04:03,117
- Help!
- [woman] Take the children!

76
00:04:03,701 --> 00:04:06,162
[gunshots]

77
00:04:06,246 --> 00:04:07,497
[grunting]

78
00:04:12,835 --> 00:04:13,795
Come on.

79
00:04:15,755 --> 00:04:16,798
Let's go.

80
00:04:21,386 --> 00:04:22,553
[grunts]

81
00:04:22,637 --> 00:04:25,848
[tense music continues]

82
00:04:28,226 --> 00:04:29,769
The mission is compromised.

83
00:04:31,604 --> 00:04:33,690
I repeat, the mission is compromised.

84
00:04:35,692 --> 00:04:36,859
[headphones thud]

85
00:04:36,943 --> 00:04:38,236
[breathing heavily]

86
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:38,903
No.

87
00:04:40,363 --> 00:04:42,573
No! This can't happen!

88
00:04:44,450 --> 00:04:48,246
- [gunshots]
- [grunting]

89
00:04:48,329 --> 00:04:51,833
[crying]

90
00:04:56,212 --> 00:04:59,716
[In Arabic] God is great!

91
00:04:59,799 --> 00:05:01,467
Datu Rahman spotted.

92
00:05:01,551 --> 00:05:02,468
Push away.

93
00:05:02,552 --> 00:05:06,180
[crying]

94
00:05:12,729 --> 00:05:14,022
[yells] Ah!

95
00:05:14,105 --> 00:05:16,190
[gunshots]

96
00:05:21,529 --> 00:05:23,865
- [screaming] Ah!
- [gunshots]

97
00:05:26,159 --> 00:05:27,410
- Sir?
- [Azuelo] Yes?

98
00:05:27,493 --> 00:05:28,536
What's wrong, Agent Angeles?

99
00:05:28,619 --> 00:05:30,330
We need to help Marcus.

100
00:05:30,413 --> 00:05:32,206
As we speak, they are being butchered,

101
00:05:32,290 --> 00:05:34,292
and they are so severely outnumbered.

102
00:05:34,375 --> 00:05:36,919
Even if we send them backup,

103
00:05:37,003 --> 00:05:38,463
they won't make it on time.

104
00:05:38,546 --> 00:05:41,257
It will take them hours to get there.

105
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:43,885
Then let's ask
for police assistance in the area!

106
00:05:43,968 --> 00:05:45,845
Negative.

107
00:05:45,928 --> 00:05:48,014
- You're not--
- It's a clandestine operation.

108
00:05:48,097 --> 00:05:50,516
So, what? You won't do anything?

109
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,893
You're really not going to do anything?!

110
00:05:51,976 --> 00:05:54,103
We have no control over the situation.

111
00:05:54,187 --> 00:05:56,355
So you're going to let Marcus
and the others die?

112
00:05:56,439 --> 00:05:58,483
Occupational hazard.

113
00:05:58,566 --> 00:05:59,984
[tense music]

114
00:06:01,235 --> 00:06:06,991
- [grunting]
- [gunshots]

115
00:06:10,536 --> 00:06:12,080
[man] God is great!

116
00:06:16,667 --> 00:06:19,587
Now, Agent Angeles,
go back to your station.

117
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:22,340
That's your best shot at saving them.

118
00:06:28,096 --> 00:06:30,473
[grunting]

119
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:38,439
[gunshots]

120
00:06:39,232 --> 00:06:40,441
[man grunts]

121
00:06:42,068 --> 00:06:43,361
Get me visuals right now.

122
00:06:43,444 --> 00:06:44,904
Boost the signal.

123
00:06:45,947 --> 00:06:47,615
[rapid gunfire]

124
00:06:55,498 --> 00:06:56,958
- [woman] Help! Help!
- [rapid gunfire]

125
00:06:58,209 --> 00:07:01,129
[fire whooshing, crackling]

126
00:07:02,964 --> 00:07:04,924
[wailing]

127
00:07:11,013 --> 00:07:15,351
[Jalil grunting]

128
00:07:19,814 --> 00:07:21,274
[Jalil] Come on!

129
00:07:23,025 --> 00:07:28,656
[coughing]

130
00:07:30,408 --> 00:07:31,701
[gunshots]

131
00:07:31,784 --> 00:07:33,619
[sinister music]

132
00:07:38,291 --> 00:07:39,792
Father!

133
00:07:39,876 --> 00:07:41,544
Wake up, Father!

134
00:07:41,627 --> 00:07:44,046
- [screams]
- [rapid gunfire]

135
00:07:47,758 --> 00:07:52,180
[people screaming]

136
00:07:57,101 --> 00:07:58,102
[breathes heavily]

137
00:08:05,776 --> 00:08:08,946
- [women screaming]
- [man shouts]

138
00:08:09,030 --> 00:08:11,657
[gunshots]

139
00:08:13,826 --> 00:08:14,785
Come on!

140
00:08:16,412 --> 00:08:19,707
[people clamoring]

141
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:22,835
[gunshots]

142
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:29,425
Hide here, okay?

143
00:08:30,134 --> 00:08:31,594
Don't leave this spot.

144
00:08:34,472 --> 00:08:35,681
[gunshots]

145
00:08:35,765 --> 00:08:37,350
[grunts] Ah! Ah!

146
00:08:38,017 --> 00:08:40,937
[wails]

147
00:08:43,439 --> 00:08:44,524
Get up.

148
00:08:45,191 --> 00:08:46,984
- [whimpers]
- [grunts]

149
00:08:49,654 --> 00:08:52,365
[grunts in pain]

150
00:08:52,448 --> 00:08:53,658
[groans loudly]

151
00:08:56,577 --> 00:08:58,913
[women screaming]

152
00:08:58,996 --> 00:09:00,957
[yells] Ah!

153
00:09:01,749 --> 00:09:03,125
Hey! Hold on!

154
00:09:03,209 --> 00:09:05,795
- [coughing]
- [flames crackling]

155
00:09:09,590 --> 00:09:13,844
- [flames roar]
- [breathing heavily]

156
00:09:13,928 --> 00:09:14,929
[grunts]

157
00:09:17,723 --> 00:09:19,600
[grunts]

158
00:09:28,901 --> 00:09:32,655
- [screaming]
- [sobbing]

159
00:09:40,329 --> 00:09:42,164
[screams] Aah!

160
00:09:43,958 --> 00:09:46,085
- Father! Father!
- What happened?

161
00:09:46,168 --> 00:09:47,503
He's alive.

162
00:09:47,587 --> 00:09:50,590
Just take him to the hospital
immediately, if you can.

163
00:09:50,673 --> 00:09:51,799
Be careful.

164
00:09:53,801 --> 00:09:55,052
Sir!

165
00:09:55,136 --> 00:09:56,137
[gunshot]

166
00:09:59,682 --> 00:10:00,808
Sir!

167
00:10:02,393 --> 00:10:06,689
- [emotional music playing]
- [gunshots]

168
00:10:14,113 --> 00:10:15,448
[screaming in the distance]

169
00:10:17,491 --> 00:10:18,951
- [gunshot]
- [grunts]

170
00:10:19,035 --> 00:10:22,788
[somber music playing]

171
00:10:29,837 --> 00:10:33,257
- [gunshots]
- [people clamoring]

172
00:10:41,891 --> 00:10:44,644
- [gunshots continue]
- [emotional music playing]

173
00:10:58,783 --> 00:10:59,825
[exhales heavily]

174
00:12:12,314 --> 00:12:14,900
- [man screaming] Ah!
- [gunshots]

175
00:12:18,779 --> 00:12:19,989
- [grunting in pain] Ah! Ah!
- [gunshots]

176
00:12:24,493 --> 00:12:27,872
[music grows dark]

177
00:12:34,545 --> 00:12:36,630
- Hey, you!
- [grunts]

178
00:12:40,551 --> 00:12:41,886
[grunts]

179
00:12:47,725 --> 00:12:48,851
Lapeña!

180
00:12:56,192 --> 00:12:58,611
[dark music continues]

181
00:13:06,952 --> 00:13:08,829
- [gunshot]
- [gasps]

182
00:13:11,081 --> 00:13:13,792
[rapid gunfire]

183
00:13:17,421 --> 00:13:18,547
[gun clicks]

184
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:23,636
[both grunting]

185
00:13:28,265 --> 00:13:29,433
[battle cry]

186
00:13:33,646 --> 00:13:37,399
- [Marcus grunting]
- [Oliver groaning]

187
00:13:38,817 --> 00:13:39,693
Just hang in there!

188
00:13:41,403 --> 00:13:45,324
[tense music continues]

189
00:13:50,079 --> 00:13:52,706
[both exclaiming]

190
00:13:54,458 --> 00:13:55,417
[grunts]

191
00:13:56,585 --> 00:13:57,753
[exclaims]

192
00:14:00,381 --> 00:14:01,757
[breathing heavily]

193
00:14:05,135 --> 00:14:07,054
[ominous music playing]

194
00:14:07,137 --> 00:14:08,222
[shouts] Aah!

195
00:14:09,890 --> 00:14:13,602
- [exclaims]
- [gunshot]

196
00:14:18,566 --> 00:14:21,777
[emotional music playing]

197
00:14:31,579 --> 00:14:33,914
[Oliver] Sir… [labored breathing]

198
00:14:33,998 --> 00:14:35,708
Before it's too late…

199
00:14:35,791 --> 00:14:38,836
[Oliver breathing raggedly]

200
00:14:38,919 --> 00:14:40,880
Please tell my family…

201
00:14:41,714 --> 00:14:44,383
that I love them deeply,
and that I will always be with them.

202
00:14:45,968 --> 00:14:47,428
[screaming in agony]

203
00:14:51,307 --> 00:14:53,350
[growling]

204
00:14:58,147 --> 00:15:00,566
[music becomes dramatic]

205
00:15:03,611 --> 00:15:07,406
- [high-pitched ringing]
- [heartbeat pounding]

206
00:15:21,629 --> 00:15:23,380
[screams]

207
00:15:23,464 --> 00:15:25,174
[breathing heavily]

208
00:15:25,257 --> 00:15:27,885
- [thrilling music playing]
- [high-pitched ringing]

209
00:15:27,968 --> 00:15:29,178
Stay with me!

210
00:15:52,785 --> 00:15:54,578
[suspenseful music playing]

211
00:15:54,662 --> 00:15:56,163
- [In Arabic] God is great!
- [Marcus] You promised--

212
00:15:57,915 --> 00:15:59,375
[both grunt]

213
00:16:01,168 --> 00:16:03,087
- [gunshot]
- [grunts]

214
00:16:06,715 --> 00:16:08,676
We had been living in peace,

215
00:16:08,759 --> 00:16:10,386
but you won't leave us alone!

216
00:16:10,469 --> 00:16:12,096
We're only after Datu Rahman.

217
00:16:15,349 --> 00:16:17,601
We didn't do anything wrong.
We didn't do anything wrong!

218
00:16:17,685 --> 00:16:19,478
[grunting, groaning]

219
00:16:20,312 --> 00:16:21,397
[growling, grunting]

220
00:16:26,151 --> 00:16:27,444
[groans]

221
00:16:28,445 --> 00:16:29,321
[grunting]

222
00:16:30,614 --> 00:16:31,865
Reroute to manual if you have to,

223
00:16:31,949 --> 00:16:33,325
I do not care!

224
00:16:33,409 --> 00:16:34,618
Get me a visual right now!

225
00:16:34,702 --> 00:16:36,787
I'm trying, ma'am!
But the signal is acting up!

226
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:39,039
I don't care! I need eyes right now!

227
00:16:40,582 --> 00:16:42,459
[groaning]

228
00:16:48,257 --> 00:16:49,383
[Jalil shouts] Aah!

229
00:16:52,136 --> 00:16:53,262
[system beeping]

230
00:16:53,345 --> 00:16:55,347
[Marcus grunting]

231
00:16:59,476 --> 00:17:00,519
[Jalil screams]

232
00:17:08,861 --> 00:17:10,446
- [breathing heavily]
- [groaning]

233
00:17:13,741 --> 00:17:17,411
- [grunts]
- [panting]

234
00:17:17,494 --> 00:17:18,537
[system beeping]

235
00:17:20,998 --> 00:17:22,124
[war cry]

236
00:17:22,207 --> 00:17:24,501
- [grunts]
- [screaming]

237
00:17:30,507 --> 00:17:32,801
[choking]

238
00:17:37,806 --> 00:17:39,767
[grunts]

239
00:17:42,352 --> 00:17:44,146
[Lara] Marcus, disengage right now!

240
00:17:46,482 --> 00:17:49,985
[grunting]

241
00:17:50,903 --> 00:17:52,154
[exhales heavily]

242
00:17:54,782 --> 00:17:56,784
Marcus, I need you to disengage right now!

243
00:17:56,867 --> 00:17:58,494
[music intensifying]

244
00:17:58,577 --> 00:18:01,789
[both grunting]

245
00:18:11,882 --> 00:18:13,675
[people sobbing,
screaming in the distance]

246
00:18:15,803 --> 00:18:17,096
Jalil!

247
00:18:18,597 --> 00:18:19,431
[gun cocks]

248
00:18:22,267 --> 00:18:24,728
[Marcus, Jalil growling]

249
00:18:27,397 --> 00:18:29,108
[Felix exclaims]

250
00:18:29,191 --> 00:18:30,609
Jalil!

251
00:18:30,692 --> 00:18:32,111
[music swelling]

252
00:18:35,155 --> 00:18:37,616
[people screaming in fear]

253
00:18:37,699 --> 00:18:40,285
[dramatic music playing]

254
00:18:50,379 --> 00:18:51,505
[explosion]

255
00:18:51,588 --> 00:18:52,965
[groans]

256
00:18:55,050 --> 00:18:56,468
Jalil…

257
00:18:57,469 --> 00:18:59,304
Why are you doing this to us?

258
00:18:59,388 --> 00:19:01,849
- [Lara] <i>Proceed to extraction point.</i>
- [sobbing]

259
00:19:01,932 --> 00:19:03,684
Tell me who gave the order.

260
00:19:03,767 --> 00:19:04,601
Say it!

261
00:19:04,685 --> 00:19:07,980
[Azuelo] <i>In our line of work,</i>
<i>death is inevitable.</i>

262
00:19:08,063 --> 00:19:12,818
[reciting prayer in Arabic]

263
00:19:18,949 --> 00:19:22,661
I chose this path to protect people.

264
00:19:22,744 --> 00:19:23,912
- [Marcus] <i>But I failed.</i>
- [mirror shatters]

265
00:19:23,996 --> 00:19:25,914
[Marcus chuckles]

266
00:19:25,998 --> 00:19:29,209
Lara, a lot of innocent people died.

267
00:19:29,293 --> 00:19:30,752
[Marcus] <i>And Harold!</i>

268
00:19:30,836 --> 00:19:32,713
- <i>Harold got left behind!</i>
- [gunshot]

269
00:19:34,131 --> 00:19:36,675
Son, what happened was not your fault.

270
00:19:38,010 --> 00:19:40,804
It could have been you who died
instead of Harold.

271
00:19:42,097 --> 00:19:44,808
And I am sure he would not want you

272
00:19:44,892 --> 00:19:46,810
to blame yourself.

273
00:19:47,644 --> 00:19:50,272
- [man] There he is!
- [woman 1] It's the criminal!

274
00:19:50,355 --> 00:19:52,316
- [man] You're a wicked man!
- [woman 1] A criminal!

275
00:19:52,399 --> 00:19:54,610
- [woman 1] Terrorist!
- [man] Spawn of the devil!

276
00:19:54,693 --> 00:19:56,445
- [woman 1] Demon!
- [woman 2] A menace to society!

277
00:19:57,362 --> 00:19:58,864
[Jamilah] <i>I will follow our father.</i>

278
00:19:58,947 --> 00:20:03,202
I cannot bear just sitting around,
doing nothing to save him.

279
00:20:03,285 --> 00:20:06,121
[music concludes]
